EBRD Will Buy Stake in Ukraine’s Insurer Universalna, IFX Says

-- B y   D a r y n a   K r a s n o l u t s k a
-- 
2011-07-12T20:54:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-12/ebrd-will-buy-stake-in-ukraine-s-insurer-universalna-ifx-says.html
The European Bank for Reconstruction
and Development will purchase a stake in Ukrainian insurer PAO
Universalna,  Interfax-Ukraine  news agency reported, citing the
bank’s Kiev office.  The London-based lender’s board of directors approved the
decision today, Interfax said without providing any details.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Daryna Krasnolutska in Kiev at 
 dkrasnolutsk@bloomberg.net ;  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
